text: int main ( void ) { int a , b ; int gcd = 0 , lcm = 0 ; int i , t ; scanf ( "%d\n" , & t ) ; while ( t -- ) { scanf ( "%d %d" , & a , & b ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= a && i <= b ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) { gcd = i ; } } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
